         <div xml:id="main">
            <head type="incipit">
               <supplied reason="XTF-compatibility">Sale ¶  June 19th '84 ¶ Baron F. v. Mueller. M.D. &amp;c ¶ Sir, ¶  ¶ I forward by parcels post some specimens of a Mentha from the bank of the Thomson River, which I have not seen here before. as I send i...</supplied>
            </head>
            <p rend="number" xml:lang="en">84.06.19</p>
            <p rend="correspondent" xml:lang="en">From Henry Niemann</p>
            <p rend="location" xml:lang="en">RB MSS M1, Library, Royal Botanic Gardens Melbourne.</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; text-align: end; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <note xml:id="ftn1" type="footnote" n="1">
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 0.3335in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3335in; font-size: 9pt; "
                     xml:lang="en">MS found with a specimen of <seg style="font-style: italic; ">
                        <name key="Ranunculus">Ranunculus</name> glabrifolius</seg> (MEL 2210293). MS annotation by M: 'Answ 20/6/84.' Letter not found.</p>
               </note>Sale<note xml:id="ftn2" type="footnote" n="2">
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 0.3335in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3335in; font-size: 9pt; "
                     xml:lang="en">Vic.; all localities mentioned in the letter are in this colony. </p>
               </note> June 19th '84</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="en">Baron F. v. Mueller. M.D. &amp;c</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="en">Sir,</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>I forward by parcels post some specimens of a <name key="Mentha">Mentha</name> from the bank of the Thomson River, which I have not seen here before. as I send impressed fresh specimens you will readily be able to perceive its peculiar odour, which is very different from that of any other labiate which has come under my observation.</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>If you will give me its name and also the name of the <name key="Ranunculus">Ranunculus</name> sent in the same parcel &amp; which is from the neighbourhood of Dandenong,</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: 0in; "
               xml:lang="en">You will greatly oblige</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: 0in; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Yours respectfully</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: 0in; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>J H Niemann</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="en">Address: —</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="en">c/o T. B. Abbott</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="en">Chemist</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="en">Sale</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="plant%20names" xml:lang="en">
               <name key="Mentha">Mentha</name>
            </p>
            <p rend="plant%20names" xml:lang="en">
               <name key="Ranunculus">Ranunculus</name>
            </p>
